Morning Star looks at this strange bot.  "Loyalty?"  he thinks to
himself,  "What IS going on here."  He decides to follow his welcome
wagon into the base.  He doesn't know if he should be with the predicons
yet, but he knows that they're definately fighting Maximals and that's
good enough for the moment.  He thinks that he isn't really afraid of
this little bug, but he doesn't want to have a two front war just yet.
